I am a customer and people-oriented change management consultant experienced in leading and implementing change initiatives during a technology and business transformation. I’m a positive, analytical and dedicated person, who is intrinsically motivated to guide others through transformation in a compassionate yet structured manner. My ability to connect with people on a personal level is what enables me to get results. 

Areas of expertise: 
- Implementation of Change Management & Digital Transformation initatives;
- Creating and implementing strategies to maximize employee adoption of change;
- Performing Stakeholder Analysis and Stakeholder Management;
- Creating and executing Communication Strategies;
- Learning & Development;
- Culture as a driver of change.

